Package: mangoro
Title: R/Go IPC using Nanomsg Next Gen
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure", 
    email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides an interface for inter-process communication (IPC) between R and Go using the Nanomsg library.
    It vendors on the Go side the mango library <https://github.com/nanomsg/mangos>
     and uses nanonext <https://github.com/r-lib/nanonext> on the R side.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
Imports: 
    processx,
    nanonext
SystemRequirements: golang (>= 1.21), GNU make
URL: https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/mangoro
BugReports: https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/mangoro/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
